sequences are NOT covered by this license and are NOT distributed in this
repository or any associated hosting platform.** This is due to:

1. Platform Terms-of-Service restrictions under data-access agreement
   DSA-2024-118 (Section 4.1 of the paper)
2. The original participant consent protocol, under which the 48
   contributing volunteers consented to research use by the original
   collecting institution, not unrestricted public redistribution

See the individual datasheets in `data/datasheets/` for full provenance,
consent, and access-restriction details.

